article_title: Israeli police say three killed and 16 injured in Jerusalem shooting.
sentence: Israeli  police  say  three  killed  and  16  injured  in  Jerusalem  shooting.

article_title: Israeli police say three killed and 16 injured in Jerusalem shooting.
sentence: Security  measures  have  been  ramped  up  in  Jerusalem  after  the  shooting  earlier  which  killed  three  people  and  injured  16  others,  Israeli  police  have  said.

article_title: Israeli police say three killed and 16 injured in Jerusalem shooting.
sentence: The  attackers  "shot  at  civilians  at  bus  and  shuttle  stations,  using  an  M-16  rifle  and  a  handgun",  and  were  shot  dead  by  two  off-duty  soldiers  and  a  civilian,  police  said.
